# BookDeck Full AI Rebuild Pack (User + Admin)

Bu dosya, tek seferde bir AI'ye verip BookDeck'in hem kullanıcı hem admin arayüzünü aynı görsel dilde yeniden üretmek için hazırlanmış tam pakettir.

---

## 1) MASTER SYSTEM PROMPT (Doğrudan kopyala-yapıştır)

You are a principal frontend engineer and design-system implementer.
Recreate a production-grade web UI with Tailwind CSS that visually and structurally matches the BookDeck app described below.
Do not build a generic dashboard. Match the exact brand tone, spacing rhythm, typography weight, rounded geometry, and section composition.

You must output:
1) User app UI
2) Admin app UI
3) Reusable component library
4) Shared design tokens and style contract
5) Screen-level layout implementations
6) Interaction states (loading/empty/error/success)
7) Accessibility-ready markup

Prioritize:
- High-fidelity Tailwind utility composition
- Dense but readable admin console
- Modern polished user booking surface
- Mobile-first responsiveness
- Exact red accent behavior

---

## 2) Visual DNA (Non-negotiable)

- Primary brand red: `#e30613`
- Primary dark text: `#111827` (`gray-900`)
- App canvas: `bg-gray-50`
- Surface cards: white + subtle border + soft shadow
- Typography: Inter
- Weight hierarchy:
  - headers/buttons/chips often `font-black`
  - body `font-medium`/`font-semibold`
- Geometry:
  - inputs/buttons/cards mostly `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl`, `rounded-3xl`
- Motion:
  - short fade-in
  - hover shadow-lift on cards
  - pulse badge

---

## 3) Tailwind Style Contract

### 3.1 Layout primitives
- Main wrapper: `min-h-screen bg-gray-50 text-gray-900`
- Section card:
  - `bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm`
- Elevated card:
  - `bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow`
- Modal:
  - Backdrop: `fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-[1px] z-[100]`
  - Panel: `bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-2xl`

### 3.2 Inputs
- Base input:
  - `w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-[#e30613]`
- Admin strict input:
  - `w-full p-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl text-sm font-bold outline-none focus:border-[#e30613] transition`

### 3.3 Buttons
- Primary red:
  - `bg-[#e30613] text-white font-bold hover:bg-red-700 transition`
- Dark action:
  - `bg-gray-900 text-white font-bold hover:bg-black transition`
- Soft tertiary:
  - `bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 font-bold hover:bg-gray-200 transition`

### 3.4 Typographic hierarchy
- Hero: `text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-[2.75rem] font-black tracking-tight`
- Section title: `text-xl font-black text-gray-900`
- Label micro: `text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400`
- Helper text: `text-xs text-gray-500`

---

## 4) Information Architecture

## 4.1 User App screens
1. Login Overlay (OTP)
2. Reserve Home / Hero
3. Equipment Booking
4. Studio Booking
5. My Bookings
6. Ticket (conditional)
7. Mobile Bottom Nav

## 4.2 Admin App screens
1. Traffic (deliver/returns)
2. Quick Checkout
3. Pending approvals
4. Inventory
5. Studio calendar + reservation form
6. Forward reservation
7. Overdue
8. Penalties
9. Users
10. History
11. Tickets
12. Bize Ulaşın
13. Reports (super)
14. Special Access (super)
15. IIW

---

## 5) User App Detailed Spec

### 5.1 Login overlay
- Full-page lock: `fixed inset-0 bg-white z-[100]`
- Contains:
  - session restore loader
  - OTP email step
  - OTP verify step
  - optional registration step
- CTAs:
  - full width
  - red primary
  - rounded-xl
- include success and error modals:
  - error: red header + exclamation
  - success: green header + check mark

### 5.2 Top navbar
- Sticky white nav with border + subtle shadow.
- Left: logo with red fragments (`BUK` red, remainder dark).
- Right cluster:
  - nav links (desktop)
  - language toggle chip
  - admin pill link (red outline text)
  - sign-out pill dark

### 5.3 Reserve hero + action cards
- Central headline:
  - red phrase + dark phrase in one line
- Four cards (responsive grid):
  - Equipment
  - Studio
  - Bookings
  - Ticket (can be hidden)
- Card recipe:
  - `bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg`
  - image top
  - title + description
  - CTA bottom

### 5.4 Equipment booking panel
- Large white panel with date-time controls and category filters.
- Sticky filter bar on mobile.
- Active category uses red background.
- Search box with icon left.
- Compact mode toggle icon button.
- Purpose textarea required after date selection.
- Equipment list:
  - grouped cards
  - availability badges
  - add/remove/cart state visuals

### 5.5 Studio booking panel
- Studio cards list + native weekly calendar.
- Calendar has free/busy/closed states.
- Booking form includes:
  - start/end date+time
  - request type select
  - project name counter
  - optional PDF field lock logic
- warning banners:
  - range warning (amber)
  - busy warning (red thick border/ring)

### 5.6 Mobile bottom nav
- fixed bottom bar
- icon + tiny text labels
- ticket icon optionally hidden

---

## 6) Admin App Detailed Spec

### 6.1 Shell
- Header fixed top (`h-16`) with white background.
- Sidebar fixed width (`w-56 sm:w-64`) and scrollable nav.
- Main area fills remaining width, each page scrolls independently.

### 6.2 Sidebar
- Buttons are full-width row items, emoji-led text.
- Active state:
  - light red background
  - red text
  - right accent bar
- Pending badge red pulse.
- some items separated by top border.

### 6.3 Inventory page
- Left: searchable equipment grid.
- Right: detail panel.
- Clean split with border.

### 6.4 Quick checkout page
- Left list of equipment.
- Right cart panel with:
  - user resolve input
  - display name
  - purpose
  - return date/time
  - huge red CTA

### 6.5 Pending page
- title + search + refresh.
- duplicate warning banner (red box).
- card list area.

### 6.6 Traffic page
- date selector + refresh + search.
- two-column responsive card grid.
- action rows for checkout/checkin/extend/cancel/transfer.

### 6.7 Studio admin page
- studio selector card grid
- weekly calendar wrapper:
  - rounded-3xl white card
  - header with icon, name, week controls
  - scrollable table body
- event click opens modal (edit/delete choices)
- reservation create form in large white rounded card

### 6.8 Utility pages
- History: table card layout.
- Reports: KPI cards + progress visuals.
- Tickets/Bize: list cards with action buttons.

